<body class="d-flex flex-column h-100 bg-light">
    <main class="flex-shrink-0">
        <!-- Projects Section-->
        <section class="py-5">
            <div class="container px-5 mb-5">
                <div class="text-center mb-5">
                    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bolder mb-0"><span class="text-gradient d-inline">Projects</span></h1>
                </div>
                <div class="row gx-5 justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-11 col-xl-9 col-xxl-8">
                      <!-- Project Card 1: Elevate App -->
                      <div class="card overflow-hidden shadow rounded-4 border-0 mb-5">
                          <div class="card-body p-0">
                              <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center">
                                  <div class="p-5 col-12 col-md-6">
                                      <h2 class="fw-bolder">Elevate App</h2>
                                      <p>Created an MVP educating young individuals in Latin America on early pregnancies and preventable illnesses. Coordinated tasks using Trello to ensure efficient workflow and timely delivery. Built and tested backend systems, implementing REST APIs for authentication and chatbot responses. Integrated Stripe for secure payment processing for appointments. Utilized PostgreSQL and API integrations to streamline data flow and enhance reliability.</p>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-center mb-4">
                                    <%= image_tag 'elevate.png', class:'img-fluid project-img', alt: 'Elevate App' %>
                                  </div>
                              </div>
                          </div>
                      </div>

                      <!-- Project Card 2: Arose AI  -->
                      <div class="card overflow-hidden shadow rounded-4 border-0 mb-5">
                          <div class="card-body p-0">
                              <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center">
                                  <div class="p-5 col-12 col-sm-6">
                                      <h2 class="fw-bolder">Arose AI App</h2>
                                      <p>Built and launched a custom website for Arose AI, an AI agency specializing in automation solutions. Created engaging visuals and optimized design for a modern, responsive user experience. Integrated Calendly for appointment scheduling and streamlined user interactions. Implemented automation features to enhance business efficiency. Currently adding payment integrations, such as Stripe, Voice Agent, and Chatbot, to help business growth.</p>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 text-center mb-4">
                                  <%= image_tag "aroseai.png", class: "img-fluid project-img", alt: "AroseAI App" %>
                                  </div>
                              </div>
                          </div>
                      </div>

                      <!-- Project Card 3: EasyCart App -->
                      <div class="card overflow-hidden shadow rounded-4 border-0 mb-5">
                          <div class="card-body p-0">
                              <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center">
                                  <div class="p-5 col-12 col-sm-6">
                                      <h2 class="fw-bolder">EasyCart App</h2>
                                      <p>Designed automated order processing workflows to optimize system efficiency and user experience. Built and tested backend workflows using REST APIs for authentication. Collaborated in an Agile environment, working with structured workflows to enhance product reliability. Integrated automated processes to streamline data flow. Enhanced front-end design using Bootstrap for a modern, responsive UI.</p>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 text-center mb-4">
                                  <%= image_tag "easycart.png", class: "img-fluid project-img", alt: "EasyCart App" %>
                                  </div>
                              </div>
                          </div>
                      </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Call to action section-->
        <section class="py-5 bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary text-white">
            <div class="container px-5 my-5">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h2 class="display-4 fw-bolder mb-4">Let's build something together</h2>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-5 py-3 fs-6 fw-bolder" href="contact.html">Contact me</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
